imdb.plot outline: Tens of thousands of Latvians at this moment are living between - regularly traveling back and forth - from Latvia to Ireland, from Ireland to Latvia. What do they search far away from home? Is it just a chance to get a job or earn more money? A lot of them hardly speaks English, even for more going to Ireland is their first time abroad. Films consist of emotional life stories of different people - documental melodramas in contemplative manner of documentary.
